{"data":[{"date":"02:30 02/07","title":"Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: \"Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 2018 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c rung chuy\u1ec3n b\u1edfi c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-190110.html\" target=\"_blank\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga</span>. Ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau khi lo\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga l\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n khi b\u00e0n thua duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Nga th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha \u0111\u1ed1t l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, c\u00e0ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc ra sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Cesc Fabregas, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng khi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00fa s\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tiki-taka thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Chelsea sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tiki-taka v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng, nh\u01b0ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. T\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm n\u1ed5i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Diego Costa v\u00e0 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Isco.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadt qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi Diego Costa t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n qua chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ea1i r\u1ed3i chuy\u1ec1n v\u1ec1 cho nhau. C\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u1eady.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i T\u00e2y Ban Nha xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, Nga s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nLa Roja ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i qu\u00e1 hai v\u00f2ng khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"795","checkdouble":"190128"},{"date":"01:48 02/07","title":"T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>La Roja ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i qu\u00e1 hai v\u00f2ng khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n n\u1eefa m\u1edbi rung chuy\u1ec3n World Cup 2018. T\u00e2y Ban Nha, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga lo\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3, v\u1edbi Koke v\u00e0 Iago Aspas l\u00e0 hai t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-463-190102.html\" target=\"_blank\">hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 1-1 trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 Hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"TBN b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 Hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>TBN b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">TBN ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111i qu\u00e1 2 v\u00f2ng khi World Cup t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018 khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u00e1m \u1ea3nh b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, La Roja ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn (k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Euro) c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i qu\u00e1 hai v\u00f2ng khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 1934, T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u00dd lo\u1ea1i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. World Cup 1966 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf Anh, h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u0103m 1982, La Roja c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111i s\u00e2u h\u01a1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng th\u1ee9 hai. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">World Cup 1990 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u00dd, h\u1ecd b\u1ecb Nam T\u01b0 lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u1ee9 th\u1ebf, World Cup 1998 t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p \u2013 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, World Cup 2006 t\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 2018 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u1edf Nga \u2013 v\u00f2ng 1/8. Th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ti\u1ebfn xa h\u01a1n khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Nam Phi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">TBN c\u1ee9 g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh\u2026 thua<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, La Roja g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 1934. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh s\u00e1ch d\u00e0i d\u1eb1ng d\u1eb7c t\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay: Brazil 1950 \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c 2002 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Nga 2018 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 v\u1eady, v\u1eadn \u0111en n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111eo b\u00e1m T\u00e2y Ban Nha sang t\u1eadn Euro th\u1eadm ch\u00ed theo m\u1ed9t d\u00e2y li\u00ean ho\u00e0n, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 Italia 1980 ngay v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Ph\u00e1p 1984 trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0110\u1ee9c 1988 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Anh 1996 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2004 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<strong><br />\r\n</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\">Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"794","checkdouble":"190129"},{"date":"04:14 02/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u2018r\u1edbt \u0111\u00e0i\u2019 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 d\u00f9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eeba b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga thua xa v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</h2><h2>Sergio Ramos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup 2018 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm x\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh l\u00ed v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean Sergio Ramos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ramos v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n La Roja cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111au kh\u1ed5 t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng. T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Penalty l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nguy hi\u1ec3m cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, h\u1ecd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Penalty kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec ch\u01a1i x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1, v\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u00e9o \u00e1o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a xem l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nga \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o t\u00f4i v\u00e0 ng\u0103n t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec n\u1eefa. VAR c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i d\u1edbp th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0&nbsp; vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i EURO 1996 v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002 c\u0169ng sau lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u may r\u1ee7i. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong n\u0103m 2004, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-461-190114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/n.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-461-190114.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-1 (pen 3-4) Nga (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau 120 ph\u00fat, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u h\u00f4m 1/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nLa Roja ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i qu\u00e1 hai v\u00f2ng khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\">Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"793","checkdouble":"190130"},{"date":"03:28 02/07","title":"HLV Hierro: \"TBN b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed7i do t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-hierro-tbn-bi-loai-khong-phai-do-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Real Madrid kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a La Roja kh\u00f4ng xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111em ra m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb v\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/tbn-sa-thai-hlv-lopetegui-ngay-truoc-them-world-cup-2018-vi-cuoc-doi-nao-may-ai-biet-truoc-421-188462.html\" target=\"_blank\">quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c</span>, sau khi \u00f4ng ngang nhi\u00ean \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi WC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi WC h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/hlv-hierro-tbn-bi-loai-khong-phai-do-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">S\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam minh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha khi \u0111\u00f3 s\u1edbm b\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u \u0111i\u1ec1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i gi\u1edd t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf t\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 La Roja r\u1ed1i ren v\u00e0 lo\u1ea1n l\u1ea1c trong khi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u201cch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y\u201d Fernando Hierro th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy nhi\u00ean, HLV Hierro ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn TBN vs Nga v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0. \u00d4ng cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cNh\u01b0 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i bu\u1ed3n t\u1ee7i khi khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u C\u0110V ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n k\u1ebb th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng chuy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean quan, nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ebb c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ea3i T\u00e2y Ban Nha xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, Nga s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\">Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"792","checkdouble":"190131"},{"date":"04:32 02/07","title":"T\u00e2y Ban Nha chia tay huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i trong tang t\u00f3c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-chia-tay-huyen-thoai-trong-tang-toc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 s\u1edbm d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n n\u1eefa m\u1edbi rung chuy\u1ec3n World Cup 2018. T\u00e2y Ban Nha, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga lo\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3, v\u1edbi Koke v\u00e0 Iago Aspas l\u00e0 hai t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau 1-1 trong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau tr\u1eadn thua Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-chia-tay-huyen-thoai-trong-tang-toc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Iniesta chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau 12 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">N\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau La Roja c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n khi huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau tr\u1eadn thua \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barcelona: \u201c\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng cho \u0110TQG trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i r\u1ed3i.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi \u0111\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 khi ng\u00e0y gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb n\u00e0y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3. Gi\u1edd th\u00ec t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1eeb t\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1y l\u00f2ng d\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c C\u0110V.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eadt tr\u00f9ng h\u1ee3p, Nga l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Iniesta trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o La Roja. Anh ra m\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu n\u0103m 2006 v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i qua 12 n\u0103m, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i qua th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i ho\u00e0ng kim nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi c\u00fap v\u00e0ng World Cup 2010 c\u00f9ng hai ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 2008 v\u00e0 2012.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh anh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2010 khi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u0103ng quang trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-hierro-tbn-bi-loai-khong-phai-do-toi-421-190131.html\">HLV Hierro: TBN b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed7i do t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\">Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"791","checkdouble":"190132"},{"date":"03:23 02/07","title":"Ramos n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 d\u00f9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eeba b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga thua xa v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</h2><h2>Sergio Ramos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ph\u1ea3i chia tay World Cup 2018 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm x\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh l\u00ed v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 8 n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean Sergio Ramos c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Tay Ban Nha\" title=\"\u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ramos v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n La Roja cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111au kh\u1ed5 t\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng. T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng minh b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Penalty l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nguy hi\u1ec3m cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, h\u1ecd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng. Penalty kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec ch\u01a1i x\u1ed5 s\u1ed1, v\u00e0 h\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thua. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng k\u00e9o \u00e1o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Real Madrid n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &quot;T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a xem l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nga \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9o t\u00f4i v\u00e0 ng\u0103n t\u00f4i ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec n\u1eefa. VAR c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i d\u1edbp th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u00e1c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, nh\u01b0&nbsp; vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh t\u1ea1i EURO 1996 v\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i World Cup 2002 c\u0169ng sau lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u may r\u1ee7i. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 thua ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong n\u0103m 2004, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1i tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-461-190114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/n.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-461-190114.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-1 (pen 3-4) Nga (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau 120 ph\u00fat, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u h\u00f4m 1/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su-421-190129.html\">T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u00e1m \u1ea3nh t\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1edfi hai l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</span><br>\r\nLa Roja ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111i qu\u00e1 hai v\u00f2ng khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u00ean ch\u00ednh Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\">Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"790","checkdouble":"190133"},{"date":"05:20 02/07","title":"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.</h2><h2>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 k\u1ef5 d\u01a1 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111em sang Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t hay kh\u00f4ng m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, tuy nhi\u00ean s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/dsc00001-0142.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00ec tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc: \u201cH\u00f4m nay ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1, t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u00e1i Lan l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 1 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn, li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u00e0 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam: \u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u01b0a th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn. \u0110\u1eafng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m cao h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eefng sai s\u1ed1 trong d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Phlippines. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra l\u00fac 15h30, ng\u00e0y 03/07.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-325-190103.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/ban-thang-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-325-190103.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nNgay l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn U19 Th\u00e1i Lan. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17-372-190078.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-thai-lan-15h30-ngay-17-372-190078.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 0-0 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan (KT): Phung ph\u00ed c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i</span><br>\r\nTr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Th\u00e1i Lan: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng video clip k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 k\u00e8m link xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"789","checkdouble":"190139"},{"date":"05:52 02/07","title":"\u0110\u1ec3 thua t\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/de-thua-tuong-moi-cua-sai-gon-hlv-nam-dinh-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ec3 thua S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 l\u1ea1i tr\u00e1ch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/HLV-VAN-SY2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb &nbsp;\u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 17 V-League b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1edbi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i BXH.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00e1 &lsquo;nh\u1ea1t&rsquo;. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi gi\u00fap cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 1-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n S\u0129 cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 tranh ch\u1ea5p, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eaft c\u00f2i nh\u01b0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t d\u1eabn t\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 h\u01a1i \u00e1c&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, d\u00f9 t\u00e2n HLV c\u1ee7a CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh C\u00f4ng&nbsp;kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi h\u1ecdp b\u00e1i nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng l\u00e0 HLV Nguy\u1ec5n Tu\u1ea5n Phong c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m vui sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;Vi\u1ec7c CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n thay HLV ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn cho t\u00e2m l\u00ed anh em c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng. Nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch c\u1edfi b\u1ecf t\u00e2m l\u00ed, ch\u01a1i \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng, v\u00e0 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"788","checkdouble":"190140"},{"date":"06:58 02/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Nga Akinfeev: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 may m\u1eafn th\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/nguoi-hung-tuyen-nga-akinfeev-chung-toi-chi-may-man-thoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng trong khung g\u1ed7 \u0110T Nga l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Akinfeev chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2>Igor Akinfeev gi\u00fap Nga l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n nhau v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-1 su\u1ed1t 120 ph\u00fat, T\u00e2y Ban Nha vs Nga \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang may r\u1ee7i. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Igor Akinfeev \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Koke v\u00e0 Aspas, trong khi De Gea l\u1ecdt l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 4 &ndash; qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i n\u00e0y, x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111i s\u00e2u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed World Cup, b\u1edfi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu x\u00e9t t\u1ea1i EURO, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 th\u1ee7 ng\u1ecdt ng\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha, khi Nga b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y lo\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft n\u0103m 2008.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Igor Akinfeev cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p may \u1edf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. \u1ede trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang. Th\u1eadt may, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n Ch\u00faa!&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Akinfeev chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" title=\"Akinfeev chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng T\u00e2y Ban Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/nguoi-hung-tuyen-nga-akinfeev-chung-toi-chi-may-man-thoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Akinfeev chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng T\u00e2y Ban Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. C\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0&hellip; \u0110T Nga, v\u00e2ng, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c C\u0110V n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 suy ngh\u0129 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec. Trong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 2 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1eddi gian hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 khung th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng k\u00e9o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, b\u1edfi \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Akinfeev chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng T\u00e2y Ban Nha, HLV Stanislav Cherchesov cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd, \u0110T Nga n\u00ean ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018-421-190133.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ramos-noi-gi-ve-that-bai-cua-tay-ban-nha-tai-world-cup-2018-421-190133.html\">Ramos n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n b\u00e3 d\u00f9 \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eeba b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga thua xa v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-461-190114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/n.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-tay-ban-nha-461-190114.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: T\u00e2y Ban Nha 1-1 (pen 3-4) Nga (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch sau 120 ph\u00fat, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ti\u1ebfp b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u h\u00f4m 1/7.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/tay-ban-nha-am-anh-tot-do-boi-hai-loi-nguyen-lich-su.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tay-ban-nha-cay-dang-tikitaka-la-thu-vo-nghia-421-190128.html\">Sao T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng: Tiki-taka l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a!</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cesc Fabregas s\u1ed1c n\u1eb7ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 TBN vs Nga khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"787","checkdouble":"190141"},{"date":"06:52 02/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (2/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/2/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-272018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 2/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u